            </svg>
          </span>
          Testing Instructions
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-300">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-purple-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">1</span>
            <p>Enter the amount you want to test (minimum â‚¹1)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-purple-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">2</span>
            <p>Click "Pay with PhonePe" to initiate the payment</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-purple-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">3</span>
            <p>You'll be redirected to PhonePe's sandbox checkout page</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-purple-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">4</span>
            <div>
